ic of their choice this will satisfy the law school's research requirement iper joint degree students who have not yet taken the course for research credit must do so in order to satisfy the joint degree requirements students who enrolled in the workshop in winter 2008 or 2009 are free to enroll in the workshop again for credit in spring 2010 this course is open to first year law school students number of units 3 course number 432 recently taught by margaret meg caldwell deborah a sivas barton h buzz thompson jr michael wara all environmental law and natural resources courses advanced environmental law clinic california coast science policy and law climate change workshop environment and energy workshop environmental law and policy environmental law clinic environmental science for managers and policy makers water law and policy related links axess coursework digital reserve sls registrar related steyer taylor center for energy policy and finance rain 57 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
